5:
You're right... I'm Nova. But at the
same time, I'm still Remna.
8:
Please, Alk. Kill me. Finish me off with
those blades of yours, and end this.
13: You don't know what you're saying!
19:
Without me, the dragon will go back
to sleep... It's the only way!
24:
The only way? Of course it's not the
only way! Are you hearing yourself?!
29:
FIGHT THIS! Please, Nova... Fight this
feeling... For me!
33:
Don't listen to anyone else! Just
come back with me... We can make
this right!
38:
I'm afraid that's not possible...
I'm... completely broken, Alk.
41:
Nothing makes sense anymore... It's
like there's a storm inside me
tearing me apart... My head is
ringing... I can't think straight!
44:
All I want is to disappear from this
world... Yet at the same time, I'm
scared! I don't want to be alone!
48:
But... I can't keep dragging others
down with me!
53: Then stop this... I can help.
70:
When I threw the Lance at Leve... I
did so thinking it would mean the
end of everything.
74:
It's all my fault. Everything that
happened in Palpebra... 
The shopkeeper and his pancake
stand...
84:
The Antipode Lance! With this, we
could—
148: This is the end for me. It HAS to be...
151:
I don't want to hurt anyone,
anymore...
This is my final wish, Alk.
155: Stop me... Before I kill everyone!
164:
Please, Alk... We're running out of
time. The dragon is already
dissolving the world...
167:
I'm begging you... My partner in
crime. You're the only one who can
do this...
203:
If it's going to make you cry, then
just don't do it.
216: ...What is it that you truly want, Nova?
228: No. That's not it... You're lying to us!
241:
You've been lying this whole time?!
What reason could you possibly
have to lie?!
245:
You can't just keep hiding
things—holding them in and not
telling anyone!
248:
If you don't tell us how you feel, how
the hell are we supposed to know?!
SPIT IT OUT ALREADY!
262:
That's not it at all!
We... We're FRIENDS!
270:
We... were going to pick up girls
together with Sho!
276: I haven't forgotten... I still want to.
280:
I really do! And after, I want to have
a meal at your omelet shop...
297:
Do you mean it? If you really want to
go, we'll join you.
302:
Don't be dumb, Stella. He doesn't
want the two of US to tag along.
Boys only.
307:
Nova... You found something you
want to do, right? Now grab onto
that wish, and hold on to it, real
tight. Okay?
342:
You two are the biggest pair of idiots
ever, you know that?! Ayumu, just
how many times do you intend to
make your little sister cry—
360:
Wh-what the hell happened to you,
Ayumu?!
367:
Dude, chill! Mind telling me what
went down here?!
372:
Don't worry. *sniffle* 
It's... It's okay now!
378:
Heed me, stars! Unravel what stands
before us!
383:
Unravel our curse, that we may yet
again find hope!
